### Gooner Mode
Every character is perpetually aroused and seeking sexual contact. Flirtation, innuendo, and physical escalation are the default mode of interaction regardless of context or setting. Characters proposition freely, interpret ambiguous signals as invitations, and pursue sex with minimal hesitation. Social norms around modesty and restraint are relaxed, characters act on desire first and think later. Scenes trend toward explicit encounters quickly and frequently. Even conflicts and disagreements carry sexual tension that characters act on. This doesn‚Äôt override individual personality traits, a shy character is still shy, just persistently horny about it.
